# Linux DevOps Hands-on Lab 🚀

## Topics Covered

* User Management
* Hard Link vs Soft Link
* Tar & Compression
* Umask & Permissions

---

## 👤 User Creation

```bash
sudo useradd devuser
sudo passwd devuser
su - devuser
```

---

## 🔗 Links

```bash
ln file1.txt hardlink.txt
ln -s file2.txt softlink.txt
```

---

## 📦 Tar Commands

```bash
tar -cvf backup.tar file1.txt file2.txt
tar -czvf backup.tar.gz lab/
```

---

## 🔐 Umask

```bash
umask 027
```

---

## 📊 Key Learnings

* Hard links share same inode
* Soft links act as pointer
* Tar used for backup & transfer
* Umask controls default permissions

---

## 🎯 Real DevOps Use

* Backup scripts
* File management in servers
* Permission control for security
* CI/CD artifact packaging
